org.matsim.contrib.socnetgen.sna.graph

Class GraphProjection<G extends Graph,V extends Vertex,E extends Edge>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.matsim.contrib.socnetgen.sna.graph.SparseGraph
      • org.matsim.contrib.socnetgen.sna.graph.GraphProjection<G,V,E>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Graph
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SampledGraphProjection

    public class GraphProjection<G extends Graph,V extends Vertex,E extends Edge>
extends SparseGraph
    This class allows to extract subgraphs from existing graphs by projecting specific vertices and edges onto a new graph. A GraphProjection works similar to a decorator, however, the connectivity of vertices and edges can differ from the original graph.
    Author:
    illenberger
